1. Basic example: basic connection and chatting from client and server
	make all
	./01.server_basic
	./01.client_basic in other terminal
	On client console, chat to server and see ACK data


2. File transfer example: client request file transfer from server
	make all
	./02.server_file_transfer
	./02.client_file_transfer in other terminal
	
	On client console:
		Type 0 to see file list
		Type 1 to add file name and request
		Insert file name and enter to send request to server
		Check file content in 02.client_result_file.txt